1617
01:36:04,906 --> 01:36:07,875
You ever heard of a casino
called Lucky Jim's?

1618
01:36:12,447 --> 01:36:14,312
Yeah.

1619
01:36:14,382 --> 01:36:15,815
Yeah, I heard of that.

1620
01:36:15,883 --> 01:36:19,478
