1657
01:37:59,320 --> 01:38:00,947
Now come on, get out of here.

1658
01:38:01,022 --> 01:38:02,649
Take a walk.

1659
01:38:13,534 --> 01:38:14,728
T.K., you okay?

1660
01:38:15,736 --> 01:38:17,761
Hey.

1661
01:38:17,838 --> 01:38:19,533
Oh, man.

1662
01:38:19,607 --> 01:38:22,132
I can't believe I almost did that.

1663
01:38:24,812 --> 01:38:25,938
I can't believe I did that.

1664
01:38:26,013 --> 01:38:28,982
Don't worry. We get it.

1665
01:38:32,553 --> 01:38:34,521
I'm sorry, guys.

1666
01:38:34,589 --> 01:38:36,318
- Don't worry about it.
